title: DNC
extract: Dilation and curettage (sometimes pronounced or spelled DNC) - a gynecological procedure. Dinitro-ortho-cresol, an herbicide. Direct numerical control or distributed numerical control, in manufacturing, a common term for networking CNC machine tools.
